And it was like this, we made public statements

00:35:07.350 --> 00:35:09.720
about how we feel about this whole thing.

00:35:09.940 --> 00:35:12.860
And I personally felt good about it back then.

00:35:12.860 --> 00:35:13.440
I still do.

00:35:13.590 --> 00:35:16.480
