00:35:16.720 --> 00:35:20.260
because either this one works out or it's not going to happen ever.

00:35:20.500 --> 00:35:22.600
We will never have a three-threaded Python ever

00:35:23.000 --> 00:35:25.260
because this is like the perfect constellation of stars.

00:35:25.440 --> 00:35:26.380
This is not coming back.

00:35:27.940 --> 00:35:28.800
